This paper is about a programming model for distributed machine learning that supports dynamic control flow. It discusses the design and implementation of the model in TensorFlow, a popular distributed machine learning system. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
